  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13067823/cycling-holidays-in-the-lakes-and-mountains-inghams.jpg" alt="Happy couple cycling in the Lakes &amp; Mountains" data-udi="umb://media/3d447fcd145244e793fd64ab0fbc0a40" /></p>
<h2>Explore Our Range of Great European Destinations by Bike</h2>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">From gentle cycle paths through flower filled meadows and along winding rivers, to steep trails criss-crossing the mountains – a <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Lakes &amp; Mountains</a> holiday is perfect for cyclists. Cycling is a popular activity in many Alpine resorts and there are an abundance of clearly marked bike trails you can explore during your holiday.</span></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 align="center"><a name="backtotop"></a>Why Cycle with Inghams</h2>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong><img src="/media/13067824/cycling-holidays-in-the-lakes-and-mountains-inghams-bikes.jpg" alt="Exploring the lakes by bike" data-udi="umb://media/24dba38e028848d2b03d74677c89fe14" /></strong></p>
<p>We recognise how popular a Lakes &amp; Mountains holiday is with cyclists.</p>
<ul>
<li>Bike hire is widely available from the sports shops in our Lakes &amp; Mountains destinations</li>
<li>Our reps will be able to recommend where you can find cycling equipment to hire</li>
<li>Many of our partner hotels offer our guests <em>free</em> bike hire</li>
<li>Few of our partner hotels provide a weekly programme of guided cycling holidays</li>
<li>Many of the local tourist offices will have maps of the local cycling routes</li>
</ul>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/holiday-types/cycling-holidays#backtotop">Back to top</a></p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
